title: Doughboys Double 24 - The First Domino with Joe Quasarano
itunes:title: Doughboys Double 24 - The First Domino with Joe Quasarano
description:
Mitch and Wiger chat with Joe Quasarano, who, as a 19-year-old college dropout, got a job as the first cook at the first ever Domino’s Pizza. But first, the ‘boys discuss the new Cheetos pop-up restaurant in NYC.
